                        levels = c('AAA', 'AA', 'A', 'B', 'C', 'D', 'E', 'F'))

# Calculating Total of Verifications 
ppd_lc$'' <- ppd_lc$'' + ppd_lc$'' + ppd_lc$'' +
                     ppd_lc$'' + ppd_lc$'' + ppd_lc$''
ppd_lc$'' <- as.numeric(ppd_lc$'')

# 
ppd_lc$'' <- (ppd_lc$'' /
                        ppd_lc$'')
ppd_lc$''[is.na(ppd_lc$'')] <- 0


# Calculating Overdue Rate 
ppd_lc$'' <- ppd_lc$'' / (ppd_lc$'' + ppd_lc$'') * 100
ppd_lc$''[is.nan(ppd_lc$'')] <- 0
ppd_lc$'' <- as.numeric(ppd_lc$'')
ppd_lc$'OverdueRate' <- ppd_lc$''

# Calculating Pay-off Rate 
ppd_lc$'PayoffRate' <- ((ppd_lc$'' - ppd_lc$'') / ppd_lc$'') * 100
ppd_lc$'PayoffRate'[is.na(ppd_lc$'PayoffRate')] <- -1

# Categorizing Pay-off Rates 
ppd_lc$'PayoffCate' <- cut(ppd_lc$'PayoffRate', 
                           breaks = c(-2, -1, 0, 99, 100), 
                           labels = c("", "", "", ""), 
                           right = TRUE)
ppd_lc$'PayoffCate' <- factor(ppd_lc$'PayoffCate', 
                              ordered = TRUE, 
                              levels = c("", "", "", ""))

# Categorizing Whether has Unpaid loans when applying 
ppd_lc$Unpaid_Total <- ppd_lc$''
ppd_lc$UnpaidCate <- NA
ppd_lc$UnpaidCate <- ifelse(ppd_lc$Unpaid_Total == 0, "", "")
ppd_lc$'UnpaidCate' <- factor(ppd_lc$'UnpaidCate', ordered = TRUE)

# Calculating Old Loan Percentage 
ppd_lc$'OldLoanPCT' <- (ppd_lc$'' / 
                          (ppd_lc$'' + ppd_lc$'')) * 100
ppd_lc$'' <- factor(ppd_lc$'')
ppd_lc$'' <- factor(ppd_lc$'')
ppd_lc$'' <- factor(ppd_lc$'')
ppd_lc$'' <- factor(ppd_lc$'')
ppd_lc$'' <- factor(ppd_lc$'')
ppd_lc$'' <- factor(ppd_lc$'')
ppd_lc$'' <- factor(ppd_lc$'')

ppd_lc_old <- subset(ppd_lc, ppd_lc$"" == 0)
ppd_lc_new <- subset(ppd_lc, ppd_lc$"" == 1)

  do(model = lm(LoanSum ~ Prev.LoanAvg, data = .))
